- "Pesan" can open chat with this seller
- "Keranjang" shows cart
- Navigation remains consistent across all pages

**Floating Elements** (if needed):
- Floating chat button (bottom-right, above nav) - optional if "Pesan" is enough
- Notification badge on "Pesan" icon if unread messages from seller

### 14. FILTER BOTTOM SHEET
**Slides up from bottom when filter button tapped:**

**Filter Options:**
- **Price Range**: Min/Max input or slider
- **Rating**: Star filter (4‚òÖ & up, 3‚òÖ & up, etc.)
- **Shipping**: Free shipping, Express, etc.
- **Discount**: On sale only toggle
- **Condition**: New, Like new, etc.
- **Sort By**: Combined with filters

**Actions:**
- "Reset" button (clears all filters)
- "Apply" button (applies and closes sheet)
- Results count preview

