## üé® MOBILE VISUAL DESIGN

### DESIGN CONSISTENCY WITH LAKU
**Match your existing design patterns:**

**From Your Current Layout:**
- **Price Display**: Red color (Rp format), bold
- **Original Price**: Gray, struck through, smaller
- **Sold Count**: "X+ terjual" format in gray
- **Product Grid**: 2 columns with consistent gap
- **Product Cards**: White background, rounded corners, clean shadows
- **Product Images**: Rounded corners, aspect ratio 3:4 or similar
- **Bottom Nav Icons**: Simple line icons with labels
- **Search Bar**: Rounded, light background, camera icon
- **Spacing**: Clean and minimal

**Store Page Design Must:**
- Use same product card styling
- Match color scheme (red for prices, gray for secondary info)
- Use same typography
- Maintain consistent spacing
- Same border radius throughout
- Button styles match existing UI
- Tab navigation follows same pattern

### Typography
- Store name: Bold, 18-20px
- Product name: 14-15px
- Price: Bold, 16-18px
- Body text: 14px
- Small text: 12-13px

### Spacing
- Page padding: 12-16px horizontal
- Section spacing: 20-24px
- Card padding: 12-16px
- Product gap: 8-12px

### Cards & Containers
- Border radius: 8-12px
- Shadows: Subtle elevation
- Store card: Slightly elevated

### Touch Targets
- Minimum: 44x44px
- Buttons: 44-48px height
- Tab height: 44-48px

### Color Zones
- Header: Solid background
- Banner: Can be colorful/branded
- Product grid: White/light background
- Cards: White with borders/shadows

---

## üîß MOBILE FUNCTIONALITY

### Store Actions
- **Follow button**: Toggle follow/unfollow
  - Animation on state change
  - Update follower count
  - Require login if not authenticated
- **Share store**: Native share or share options
- **Chat**: Open conversation with seller

### Product Interactions
- **Tap product card**: Navigate to product page
- **Long press** (optional): Quick actions (add to cart, wishlist)
- **Image tap**: Direct to product

### Filtering & Sorting
- **Filter button**: Open bottom sheet
- **Sort dropdown**: Select sort option, reload grid
- **Quick filter chips**: Tap to activate, reload
- **Multiple filters**: Apply together

### Infinite Scroll
- Auto-load when user reaches bottom
- Loading indicator
- "End of results" message when done

### Tab Navigation
- **Tap tab**: Activate and scroll to content
- **Swipe left/right** (optional): Navigate between tabs
- Active state visible

### Review Interactions
- **Expand review**: Tap to see full text
- **View images**: Tap to open gallery
- **Helpful button**: Increment, visual feedback
- **Read seller reply**: Expandable

