## üìä MOBILE DATA STRUCTURE

### Store Object
```typescript
{
  id: string
  name: string
  logo: string
  banner: string
  verified: boolean
  rating: number
  productCount: number
  followers: number
  description: string
  stats: {
    totalSales: string
    repurchaseRate: string
    qualityScore: number
    shippingScore: number
    serviceScore: number
    responseRate: number
    shipOnTimeRate: number
  }
  badges: string[]
  location: string
  joinedDate: Date
  policies: {
    return: string
    shipping: string
  }
  products: Product[]
  categories: Category[]
  reviews: Review[]
}
```

### Category Object
```typescript
{
  id: string
  name: string
  icon?: string
  productCount: number
  subcategories?: Category[]
}
```

